Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.42,0:00:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让你久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.94,0:00:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.27,0:00:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生气啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.17,0:00:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦 怎么在拍我呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.82,0:00:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛偷拍人家啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.68,0:00:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想留个纪念嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且我还特意买了台好相机哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.99,0:00:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.60,0:00:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也超可爱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.88,0:00:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍出来可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.36,0:00:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,精神不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.43,0:00:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就好，好期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.27,0:00:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.86,0:00:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次要去稍微远点的地方 没关系吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.89,0:00:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没关系的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是一起去嘛 而且只有我们两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.28,0:00:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去车站里逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.89,0:01:01.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,离新干线发车还有点时间
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去随便转转吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.17,0:01:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢 肚子饿不饿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.26,0:01:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不饿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.84,0:01:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早上吃过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.55,0:01:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没吃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.98,0:01:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过我口渴了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.38,0:01:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,口渴啦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.48,0:01:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还挺会撒娇的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.13,0:01:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.23,0:01:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边好像有家咖啡店
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.67,0:01:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真是诶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.75,0:01:33.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.96,0:01:43.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想喝的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.10,0:01:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,种类还挺多的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.73,0:01:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有伯爵茶之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.20,0:01:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着好精致啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要伯爵茶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:55.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打包带走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:01:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,热的伯爵茶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.24,0:02:00.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,热伯爵茶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.34,0:02:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来两杯伯爵茶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.64,0:02:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.93,0:02:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接拿着没问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.68,0:02:08.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, 可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.66,0:02:10.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮我拿一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.44,0:02:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.48,0:02:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请问有积分卡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有 不需要了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.26,0:02:30.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然打包了 要不还是坐会儿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.39,0:02:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在刚过11点呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.86,0:02:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在大概几点了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.46,0:02:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还有大概30分钟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.17,0:02:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,时间还挺充裕的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.47,0:02:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这卡片挺可爱的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.81,0:02:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很可爱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.77,0:02:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好想要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:02:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包装好像挺好看的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.25,0:03:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱，挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.47,0:03:09.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把你手跟我的手一起拍一张怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.02,0:03:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留个纪念
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.95,0:03:24.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是不是怕烫来着，猫舌头吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是猫舌头
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 明明就是嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.65,0:03:29.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你吃不了拉面之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拉面倒还好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都不记得了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.59,0:03:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开玩笑的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.01,0:03:55.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的随便挑哦，买几个都行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.47,0:03:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全买下来也可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个好不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉分量刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.57,0:04:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就买两个这个吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.61,0:04:32.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在那边最近的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买完就很满足了 准备去坐新干线咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.32,0:04:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上车啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.84,0:04:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快点快点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.58,0:04:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.67,0:04:59.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上车了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.51,0:05:02.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:09.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.84,0:05:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到新横滨了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.20,0:05:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不错哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.80,0:05:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真开心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.66,0:05:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.56,0:05:59.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.44,0:06:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去仲见世街逛逛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,温泉街上肯定有很多店
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.10,0:06:16.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该也有很多好吃的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.04,0:06:21.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你吃饱了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过如果有想吃的东西要跟我说哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.52,0:06:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,应该在营业吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炸黄油？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.48,0:06:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 是在排队吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.50,0:06:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真是诶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.08,0:06:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家在排什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.21,0:06:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,人好多啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.06,0:06:52.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 就这里人特别多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.41,0:06:54.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么东西 要过去看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.66,0:07:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么呀 到底在排什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.76,0:07:04.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,估计是很有名吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.94,0:07:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.89,0:07:12.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,亏你能找到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.09,0:07:16.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.18,0:07:20.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不太喜欢吃红豆馅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:21.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.20,0:07:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.58,0:07:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前都不知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.42,0:07:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实 不知道你讨厌吃什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.93,0:07:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来你不太喜欢红豆馅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.54,0:07:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特别讨厌带颗粒的那种
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.12,0:07:47.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要买点什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍出来会好看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糖果？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.98,0:07:55.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪个哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是糖果嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.98,0:07:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是很可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.94,0:08:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为很可爱嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.50,0:08:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.54,0:08:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面夹了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.38,0:08:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺新奇的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.74,0:08:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,买这个可以吗 这个糖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.28,0:08:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗 想要哪个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.39,0:08:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,草莓糖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能给我拿两个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.48,0:08:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.26,0:08:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:40.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很大哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.54,0:08:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.04,0:08:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 一起吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.66,0:08:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好大啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.98,0:09:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉特别棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是怎么做的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好甜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.16,0:09:20.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点甜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.26,0:09:25.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个 不咬到草莓就没味道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糖衣裹得太厚了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.64,0:09:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微来一点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.38,0:09:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.52,0:09:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咬开了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛 小心点
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.25,0:10:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 我来帮你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.03,0:10:07.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个一口吃一个会不会太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.85,0:10:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过里面是草莓吧 把它拔出来的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.36,0:10:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直都好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:20.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是草莓，好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:45.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忘了拍照了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恋人专座
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面有钱 可以投进去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.82,0:11:24.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一 二
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.08,0:11:29.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,愿望成真
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.50,0:11:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄湿了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.84,0:12:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.17,0:12:09.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.83,0:12:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会有鱼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.32,0:12:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 有好多
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.98,0:12:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在呢 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:19.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,厉害厉害 哇好兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.62,0:12:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.58,0:12:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像水族馆一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有条好大的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想拍个视频
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.35,0:12:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,请拍请拍
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来这边 过来
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍到了 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.82,0:12:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坐下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:56.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,据说不投钱就看不到外面呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.76,0:13:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不游过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.22,0:13:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也尝一点吧 给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.39,0:13:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.23,0:14:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看这温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.15,0:14:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,热气腾腾的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.35,0:14:05.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.96,0:14:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.26,0:14:17.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大吗 好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.05,0:14:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比想象中还要大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:22.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房间也挺大的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.50,0:14:25.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉能好好放松一下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.97,0:14:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.30,0:14:31.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.80,0:14:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 突然这样没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,居然还有这么精致的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.63,0:14:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鞋子都摆好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛 这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.18,0:14:54.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉挺好 比想象的还要好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.56,0:14:58.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久没出来玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.60,0:15:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.40,0:15:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挑了个好地方 真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:09.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错嘛 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,累了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.14,0:15:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然累但很开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.11,0:15:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:20.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉今天一直都很开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.99,0:15:24.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天很悠闲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.73,0:15:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你害羞什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.92,0:15:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为进了房间变安静了 有点……
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.76,0:15:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.90,0:15:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.93,0:15:39.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你总是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过你这点倒是挺可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.62,0:15:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为换了个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:47.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才会这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,忍不住想把你换衣服的样子拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.45,0:16:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,外套我帮你拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.89,0:16:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.97,0:16:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也在这儿脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.61,0:16:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在这儿啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.06,0:16:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拍得太近了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.84,0:16:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太近了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.19,0:17:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.85,0:17:04.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还挺害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.69,0:17:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在是不是超害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.63,0:17:11.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是因为在拍吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.18,0:17:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为平时都不拍的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.88,0:17:14.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛呀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是很奇怪吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.59,0:17:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪？ 很奇怪啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.08,0:17:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.37,0:17:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是故意脱得这么性感的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才没有呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.57,0:17:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点新鲜感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.63,0:17:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像是在被你撩拨一样
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.49,0:18:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点冷
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.40,0:18:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱的内衣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.73,0:18:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水蓝色的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.16,0:18:14.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点不妙 突然有点兴奋了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.91,0:18:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,懂了 我来拍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.59,0:18:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我拍拍你穿内衣的样子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.61,0:18:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.74,0:18:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉我像个变态一样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.61,0:18:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本来就像个变态嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.19,0:18:54.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为只有小文脱了 我也只能脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.26,0:19:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.70,0:19:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 别学我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.73,0:19:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.08,0:19:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱吧 真性感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.95,0:19:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.60,0:19:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次见这条内裤
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.90,0:19:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这条吗 为了今天特意买的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.98,0:19:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.32,0:19:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,躺下咯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.55,0:19:41.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 玻璃挺干净的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.60,0:19:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞 抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.28,0:20:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.16,0:20:07.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定很暖和 肯定很暖和哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.74,0:20:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里可能会有点冷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来才是重头戏哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:16.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么重头戏
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.50,0:20:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.55,0:20:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错吧 在地板上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.43,0:20:31.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超级舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.55,0:20:40.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你现在的表情最迷人了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.86,0:20:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才肯定很冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.90,0:20:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,风也很大呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:20:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是奖励吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:20:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算不上奖励吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.83,0:21:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是奖励哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.05,0:21:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天真的好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.35,0:21:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.34,0:21:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在海鸥下面看到了好多宝贝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.97,0:21:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个挺不错的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.13,0:21:15.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到会有那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.09,0:21:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉像特别的衣服 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.57,0:21:27.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.83,0:21:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这调皮鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.12,0:21:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.45,0:21:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,生气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.97,0:22:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天是不是还没亲过
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.56,0:22:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是没亲过呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.39,0:22:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算不亲亲…… 不亲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.57,0:22:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,坏心眼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.46,0:22:39.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,状态回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.02,0:22:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恢复了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.20,0:23:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一接吻开关就打开了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.86,0:23:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的表情总是会变
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.90,0:23:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会变吗 恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.87,0:23:47.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样好害羞 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:51.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.62,0:24:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个真不得了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.67,0:24:45.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一进房间就开始了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.38,0:25:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超级舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.99,0:25:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天不是有带吗
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.74,0:26:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 给我舔舔
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.56,0:26:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来 看这边
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.02,0:26:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.53,0:26:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是开关嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.01,0:26:51.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让人欲罢不能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.54,0:27:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恢复到不错的状态了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.12,0:27:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的姿势好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.29,0:28:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,声音很大嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.87,0:28:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.70,0:28:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很暖和
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.13,0:28:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让我喝下去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.26,0:29:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.46,0:30:03.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿着这个
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.80,0:30:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.04,0:30:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都看光了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.24,0:30:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湿得一塌糊涂了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.66,0:30:41.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.66,0:30:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变得好热啊
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.34,0:30:48.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进到里面去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.30,0:30:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉要热晕了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.32,0:31:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么弄得乱七八糟的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.94,0:31:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,系好了吗 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.90,0:31:21.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这不是马上就脱落了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.12,0:31:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.54,0:31:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本性暴露了吧 粗枝大叶的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.36,0:31:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就一点点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.85,0:31:38.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然插进去了 但果然还是……
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.41,0:31:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.36,0:31:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢这个对吧 喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.78,0:32:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就脱落了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.71,0:32:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用强忍着
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.85,0:32:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.91,0:33:10.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看 因为你稍微舔了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.19,0:33:17.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太敏感了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.75,0:33:21.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小文 看不清楚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.70,0:33:36.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就叫出声了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.01,0:33:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说什么呢 叫得超大声的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.48,0:33:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.78,0:33:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,血液循环变好了 变得更舒服了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.13,0:34:25.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.36,0:34:34.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真色情
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.43,0:34:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要咬吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.77,0:34:52.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.14,0:35:26.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.52,0:35:43.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天不是很厉害吗 这状态
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.34,0:35:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:35:57.20,0:36:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不厉害吗 和平时一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.20,0:36:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明就是平时的样子嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.56,0:36:17.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.71,0:36:19.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把手拿开？
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.93,0:36:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好暖和啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.37,0:36:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,暖和吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.68,0:36:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你自己摸摸看
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.00,0:37:07.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才喷水了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.96,0:37:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.14,0:37:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.69,0:38:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.70,0:39:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.55,0:39:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.51,0:39:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.38,0:39:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一直露出一副色色的表情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.00,0:39:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.83,0:40:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢你这个表情
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.68,0:41:11.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.74,0:41:21.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有点疼
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.39,0:41:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.51,0:42:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:03.43,0:42:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在看对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.63,0:42:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.32,0:42:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,眼神对上就会很兴奋
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.62,0:42:11.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对上眼就会兴奋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.78,0:42:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不喜欢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.78,0:42:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别关灯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.77,0:43:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.67,0:45:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄疼你了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.27,0:45:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.56,0:45:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.57,0:45:25.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看上去一副想让我舔的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.33,0:47:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那里好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:47:19.69,0:47:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又躺下了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.93,0:47:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我动了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.33,0:48:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你可以自己动哦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.89,0:48:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我自己动
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.40,0:48:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.73,0:48:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在动了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.49,0:48:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一笑就会进空气啦
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.32,0:48:33.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事哦 来 动起来
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.50,0:48:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你笑什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.56,0:48:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害 很厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.10,0:48:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一笑就有空气进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.90,0:48:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过挺可爱的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.28,0:49:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面都进空气了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.71,0:49:02.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞啦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.02,0:49:09.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,弄弄我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.52,0:49:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.20,0:49:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变得很敏感了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.18,0:50:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.88,0:50:20.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽翻了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.96,0:50:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.07,0:52:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很享受吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.87,0:52:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很享受
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.57,0:52:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃到头发了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.60,0:53:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,契合吗
Dialogue: 0,0:53:42.94,0:53:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天也好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:54:35.31,0:54:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变大了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.12,0:54:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.54,0:54:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.99,0:56:19.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真要命
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.03,0:56:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能躺下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:39.48,0:56:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以在这里睡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.72,0:56:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.44,0:58:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.72,0:58:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.53,0:58:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.94,0:59:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很色吗
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.88,1:00:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.50,1:01:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一舔你反应就好大
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.40,1:01:03.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.36,1:01:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能拍下来吗
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.32,1:01:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又要硬了嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.69,1:04:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要硬了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.19,1:04:53.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,软不回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.24,1:05:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.22,1:06:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.38,1:06:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.64,1:06:16.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.36,1:06:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:06:28.84,1:06:30.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.19,1:07:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.59,1:08:06.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微动一下
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.89,1:08:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稍微动一动
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.41,1:08:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行吗
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.59,1:08:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.74,1:08:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样插着
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.14,1:08:54.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣服掉了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.27,1:08:55.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个已经不需要了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.35,1:08:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干脆脱了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:08:56.91,1:08:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,脱了继续吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.25,1:10:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:10:03.87,1:10:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢这样 最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:46.39,1:10:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,女孩子的那里好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:11:03.64,1:11:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最喜欢了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:40.46,1:11:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.86,1:11:50.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗 怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.66,1:11:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:11:56.04,1:11:57.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爽吗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.94,1:12:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样爽吗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:04.04,1:12:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.29,1:12:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在发抖吗
Dialogue: 0,1:12:37.27,1:12:38.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.86,1:12:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看不见
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.36,1:12:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个你要自己弄吗
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.89,1:13:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好辛苦
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.66,1:14:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.48,1:14:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.58,1:14:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢吗
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.89,1:14:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.14,1:14:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 要起来吗
Dialogue: 0,1:14:42.60,1:14:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太猛了
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.82,1:14:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样行吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:03.20,1:15:04.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.37,1:15:05.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好害羞
Dialogue: 0,1:15:15.04,1:15:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水声响个不停呢
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.88,1:15:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我真的好喜欢这样
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.13,1:15:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样吗
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.48,1:15:31.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.58,1:16:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.56,1:16:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.90,1:16:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.28,1:17:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是欲罢不能呢
Dialogue: 0,1:17:25.73,1:17:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是停不下来
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.43,1:17:28.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不去吗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:29.35,1:17:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么表情呀
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.42,1:17:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像还不行
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.60,1:17:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能稍微有点受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.40,1:17:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:45.70,1:17:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,1:17:49.86,1:17:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再稍微激烈一点也可以吗
Dialogue: 0,1:17:53.42,1:17:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,1:18:03.32,1:18:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,彻底受不了了
Dialogue: 0,1:18:17.49,1:18:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.79,1:18:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,翻个身
Dialogue: 0,1:19:03.24,1:19:06.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好难受
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.88,1:19:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.95,1:19:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.71,1:19:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.16,1:19:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不给你
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.78,1:19:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了吗
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.06,1:19:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 马上就要去了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:19:43.74,1:19:45.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.16,1:19:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射在里面咯
Dialogue: 0,1:19:50.10,1:19:52.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.03,1:20:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉比平时射得都多
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.31,1:20:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟做了那么久嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.90,1:20:39.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是 有点憋太久了
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.29,1:20:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攒了很久吗
Dialogue: 0,1:20:45.03,1:20:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,特意攒着的 好开心
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.43,1:20:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.93,1:20:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了很多出来对吧
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.15,1:20:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.79,1:24:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,终于醒了
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.41,1:24:38.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,1:24:41.25,1:24:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么拿着摄像机啊 等一下
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.75,1:24:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,干嘛拍这个呀
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.25,1:24:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是觉得好玩
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.53,1:24:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.39,1:24:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从什么时候开始拍的
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.47,1:25:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.35,1:27:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变大了 不得了
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.28,1:27:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以插进去吗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.50,1:27:17.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面会疼吗
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.96,1:27:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你的里面
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.82,1:27:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湿湿滑滑的哦
Dialogue: 0,1:27:41.02,1:27:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.56,1:28:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,1:28:37.58,1:28:40.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,1:29:39.87,1:29:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗
Dialogue: 0,1:29:57.61,1:30:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大早上就这么辛苦呢
Dialogue: 0,1:45:13.44,1:45:15.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,2:00:50.22,2:00:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉和放在外面的完全不一样大 吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,2:00:58.16,2:00:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过今天天气晴朗真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,2:00:59.74,2:01:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 昨天还说会很暖和
Dialogue: 0,2:01:01.94,2:01:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺暖和的
Dialogue: 0,2:01:07.30,2:01:10.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶 吃草莓你会蘸什么
Dialogue: 0,2:01:11.52,2:01:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炼乳以外的吗
Dialogue: 0,2:01:14.46,2:01:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如 蘸味噌？
Dialogue: 0,2:01:17.08,2:01:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,2:01:20.74,2:01:24.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,味噌？ 你试过蘸味噌吃吗
Dialogue: 0,2:01:24.63,2:01:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,2:01:26.18,2:01:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺好吃的哦
Dialogue: 0,2:01:29.36,2:01:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,炼乳、味噌 还有巧克力的
Dialogue: 0,2:01:34.13,2:01:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧克力糖浆
Dialogue: 0,2:01:36.88,2:01:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,说到巧克力……诶 我从小吃草莓就蘸盐
Dialogue: 0,2:01:43.07,2:01:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,2:01:45.50,2:01:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃草莓从来都只蘸盐
Dialogue: 0,2:01:49.15,2:01:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,2:01:49.81,2:01:51.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,2:01:51.63,2:01:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经常会让人吃一惊 朋友们也是
Dialogue: 0,2:01:53.96,2:01:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次听说吗
Dialogue: 0,2:01:56.40,2:01:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么会这样呢
Dialogue: 0,2:01:58.50,2:02:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉撒点盐什么都好吃
Dialogue: 0,2:02:01.96,2:02:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能引出食材本身的鲜味嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:02:04.30,2:02:05.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对
Dialogue: 0,2:02:05.84,2:02:08.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有吃西瓜才会撒盐吧
Dialogue: 0,2:02:08.90,2:02:11.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像西柚也会撒盐啊
Dialogue: 0,2:02:11.60,2:02:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盐吗
Dialogue: 0,2:02:13.58,2:02:15.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没听说过吗
Dialogue: 0,2:02:15.06,2:02:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是撒糖吗
Dialogue: 0,2:02:18.86,2:02:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可能是撒糖吧
Dialogue: 0,2:02:24.10,2:02:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,盐和糖可完全不一样啊
Dialogue: 0,2:02:27.08,2:02:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是糖吗
Dialogue: 0,2:02:30.22,2:02:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 我也不太清楚 还没试过撒盐吃呢
Dialogue: 0,2:02:44.03,2:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样开车兜风
Dialogue: 0,2:02:48.19,2:02:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺向往的
Dialogue: 0,2:03:32.19,2:03:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你睡着了吧
Dialogue: 0,2:03:34.83,2:03:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全没注意到
Dialogue: 0,2:03:36.74,2:03:38.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的呀
Dialogue: 0,2:03:38.79,2:03:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我说过到了会叫你的嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:03:42.63,2:03:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吓了一跳
Dialogue: 0,2:03:44.68,2:03:46.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡相超可爱的
Dialogue: 0,2:03:49.09,2:03:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为太暖和了 不小心就睡着了
Dialogue: 0,2:03:59.25,2:04:00.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,2:04:01.89,2:04:04.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,结了好多草莓呢
Dialogue: 0,2:04:04.97,2:04:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:04:14.86,2:04:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久没来采草莓了
Dialogue: 0,2:04:17.07,2:04:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,2:04:23.82,2:04:25.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好多啊
Dialogue: 0,2:04:25.03,2:04:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉真不错
Dialogue: 0,2:04:30.14,2:04:31.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是很大 这个有点
Dialogue: 0,2:04:31.53,2:04:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的哎
Dialogue: 0,2:04:33.50,2:04:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,2:04:38.98,2:04:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摘起来会很难吗
Dialogue: 0,2:04:41.92,2:04:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个绝对不能放下来吧
Dialogue: 0,2:04:43.99,2:04:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 我拿着呢
Dialogue: 0,2:04:52.15,2:04:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样
Dialogue: 0,2:05:00.64,2:05:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错呢
Dialogue: 0,2:05:01.34,2:05:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好大 真大啊
Dialogue: 0,2:05:10.62,2:05:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个能直接吃吗
Dialogue: 0,2:05:13.00,2:05:15.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蘸着吃也行 就直接吃吧
Dialogue: 0,2:05:15.65,2:05:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,2:05:26.98,2:05:28.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好险
Dialogue: 0,2:05:28.23,2:05:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好甜
Dialogue: 0,2:05:30.30,2:05:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃！ 好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,2:05:33.06,2:05:34.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很不错嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:05:35.38,2:05:36.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个好大
Dialogue: 0,2:05:36.15,2:05:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪个
Dialogue: 0,2:05:37.80,2:05:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的好大 好红
Dialogue: 0,2:05:39.08,2:05:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,红的那些 感觉这边的都不错吧
Dialogue: 0,2:05:42.59,2:05:44.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对 红通通的 绝对很甜
Dialogue: 0,2:05:44.92,2:05:46.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好好吃
Dialogue: 0,2:05:46.20,2:05:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒好棒
Dialogue: 0,2:05:53.55,2:05:55.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不错 大口吃的感觉
Dialogue: 0,2:05:55.14,2:05:56.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太可爱了
Dialogue: 0,2:05:56.68,2:05:58.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来好幸福
Dialogue: 0,2:05:58.12,2:06:00.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿太多了
Dialogue: 0,2:06:00.79,2:06:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事 我吃这边的
Dialogue: 0,2:06:02.52,2:06:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是吃不下的话
Dialogue: 0,2:06:05.64,2:06:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我努力吃
Dialogue: 0,2:06:13.01,2:06:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面的也很好看
Dialogue: 0,2:06:21.88,2:06:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那边那些看起来很不错
Dialogue: 0,2:06:25.53,2:06:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对对 那一块 真的哎
Dialogue: 0,2:06:32.32,2:06:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尝不出什么区别呢
Dialogue: 0,2:06:33.91,2:06:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都很好吃对吧
Dialogue: 0,2:06:36.21,2:06:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都好吃
Dialogue: 0,2:06:38.60,2:06:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,2:06:39.71,2:06:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也有长得奇形怪状的呢
Dialogue: 0,2:06:43.82,2:06:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着好像不太好吃的样子
Dialogue: 0,2:06:46.94,2:06:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像脚一样
Dialogue: 0,2:06:48.25,2:06:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,2:06:49.12,2:06:52.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉有点色色的呢
Dialogue: 0,2:06:54.50,2:06:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像屁股？
Dialogue: 0,2:06:55.52,2:06:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对对对 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,2:07:13.02,2:07:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看着好幸福
Dialogue: 0,2:07:19.53,2:07:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,2:07:20.81,2:07:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,2:07:33.67,2:07:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个真的是吗 感觉不错吧
Dialogue: 0,2:07:35.54,2:07:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉就是纯正的草莓味
Dialogue: 0,2:07:37.09,2:07:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃到了纯正的草莓
Dialogue: 0,2:07:51.34,2:07:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,2:07:57.70,2:07:59.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肯定很好吃
Dialogue: 0,2:08:00.66,2:08:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃 太好了
Dialogue: 0,2:08:04.20,2:08:05.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真不错
Dialogue: 0,2:08:21.74,2:08:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是有拿手的绝活嘛 试一下
Dialogue: 0,2:08:25.26,2:08:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进哪边好呢
Dialogue: 0,2:08:27.88,2:08:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,2:08:55.98,2:08:57.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝对很好吃
Dialogue: 0,2:08:57.28,2:08:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪个
Dialogue: 0,2:08:59.44,2:09:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,樱花虾
Dialogue: 0,2:09:01.94,2:09:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为你是看着那个说的呢
Dialogue: 0,2:09:03.32,2:09:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个超大的
Dialogue: 0,2:09:05.96,2:09:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个绝了啊
Dialogue: 0,2:09:14.30,2:09:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不买一个那个试试
Dialogue: 0,2:09:15.91,2:09:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,给大家
Dialogue: 0,2:09:19.28,2:09:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当伴手礼给大家带回去不就好了
Dialogue: 0,2:09:51.90,2:09:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你吃得可真香啊
Dialogue: 0,2:09:55.70,2:09:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,2:10:10.68,2:10:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然和普通的水族馆有点不一样呢
Dialogue: 0,2:10:13.74,2:10:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉是不太一样呢
Dialogue: 0,2:10:17.90,2:10:18.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:10:18.99,2:10:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是不是在吃东西
Dialogue: 0,2:10:20.05,2:10:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是吗 在吃呢
Dialogue: 0,2:10:32.74,2:10:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉手上破了个洞
Dialogue: 0,2:10:34.32,2:10:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪里哪里
Dialogue: 0,2:10:36.66,2:10:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的哎
Dialogue: 0,2:10:40.68,2:10:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉里面空空的
Dialogue: 0,2:10:44.56,2:10:46.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你这话说得有点过分哦
Dialogue: 0,2:10:46.39,2:10:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面黑黑的
Dialogue: 0,2:10:49.94,2:10:52.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全是没见过的 根本认不出来啊
Dialogue: 0,2:10:52.33,2:10:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是认不出来
Dialogue: 0,2:10:53.62,2:10:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉没有那些常见的品种
Dialogue: 0,2:10:56.05,2:10:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,常见的是什么
Dialogue: 0,2:10:57.80,2:10:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,会是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,2:11:00.84,2:11:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,常见的品种啊…… 水母
Dialogue: 0,2:11:03.92,2:11:06.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错啊 水母果然很不错呢
Dialogue: 0,2:11:06.92,2:11:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看这边
Dialogue: 0,2:11:09.98,2:11:11.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,水母
Dialogue: 0,2:11:18.91,2:11:23.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要再找个地方休息一下
Dialogue: 0,2:11:23.61,2:11:25.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去！
Dialogue: 0,2:11:39.90,2:11:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得很厉害吗 为什么是这个楼梯
Dialogue: 0,2:11:41.72,2:11:42.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:11:42.76,2:11:45.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种桌子挺少见的
Dialogue: 0,2:11:45.21,2:11:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺时尚的呢
Dialogue: 0,2:11:47.47,2:11:49.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等 等等
Dialogue: 0,2:11:52.98,2:11:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,2:11:56.36,2:11:58.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,2:11:59.18,2:12:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,2:12:06.73,2:12:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,2:12:08.21,2:12:09.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情趣酒店里有这个
Dialogue: 0,2:12:09.53,2:12:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么 机器吗
Dialogue: 0,2:12:12.42,2:12:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是美黑机吗
Dialogue: 0,2:12:14.21,2:12:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,美黑机？
Dialogue: 0,2:12:15.40,2:12:17.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你完全沾不上边吧
Dialogue: 0,2:12:18.42,2:12:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是钻进去烤的吧
Dialogue: 0,2:12:20.20,2:12:21.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这样吗
Dialogue: 0,2:12:21.29,2:12:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要么就是某种能缓解疲劳的太空舱吧
Dialogue: 0,2:12:28.04,2:12:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是有的话真想进去躺躺
Dialogue: 0,2:12:35.58,2:12:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过氛围挺好的
Dialogue: 0,2:12:37.42,2:12:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好宽敞
Dialogue: 0,2:12:38.26,2:12:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,2:12:46.66,2:12:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么东西哦
Dialogue: 0,2:12:48.49,2:12:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,2:12:51.52,2:12:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然出现个这东西 挺吓人的
Dialogue: 0,2:12:53.54,2:12:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吓我一跳
Dialogue: 0,2:12:56.11,2:12:57.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁会用啊
Dialogue: 0,2:12:57.30,2:12:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只能试试看了嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:12:58.53,2:13:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都在变呢
Dialogue: 0,2:13:03.18,2:13:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你不是喜欢那个嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:13:05.05,2:13:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不喜欢呢
Dialogue: 0,2:13:07.60,2:13:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我都没用过哦
Dialogue: 0,2:13:19.77,2:13:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们在这边待的时间快到了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:13:22.11,2:13:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快结束了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:13:22.83,2:13:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然来这里只是为了稍微休息一下
Dialogue: 0,2:13:29.69,2:13:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺开心的
Dialogue: 0,2:13:31.18,2:13:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,2:13:33.41,2:13:35.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉又有点舍不得了
Dialogue: 0,2:13:36.17,2:13:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,2:13:39.41,2:13:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像这样一直待在一起 也好久没有了吧
Dialogue: 0,2:13:57.58,2:13:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自动贩卖机？
Dialogue: 0,2:14:06.44,2:14:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,2:14:09.42,2:14:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这点倒是挺有情趣酒店的特色呢
Dialogue: 0,2:14:13.00,2:14:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,混了好多东西呢
Dialogue: 0,2:14:17.74,2:14:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什么 Cosplay吗
Dialogue: 0,2:14:19.57,2:14:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有Cosplay吗
Dialogue: 0,2:14:20.42,2:14:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还真是
Dialogue: 0,2:14:25.64,2:14:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么 第一次听说
Dialogue: 0,2:14:27.75,2:14:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好奇吗
Dialogue: 0,2:14:28.68,2:14:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要不要给你买个什么
Dialogue: 0,2:14:35.62,2:14:37.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是润滑液和跳蛋
Dialogue: 0,2:14:37.97,2:14:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢跳蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,2:14:38.94,2:14:41.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢
Dialogue: 0,2:14:44.01,2:14:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就买了
Dialogue: 0,2:14:48.37,2:14:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,2:14:51.37,2:14:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跳蛋之类的…… 不对 是润滑液
Dialogue: 0,2:14:53.99,2:14:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,润滑液？ 姑且先拿出来了
Dialogue: 0,2:14:55.79,2:14:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要拿走吗
Dialogue: 0,2:14:56.73,2:14:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿走
Dialogue: 0,2:15:00.41,2:15:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺可爱的嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:15:02.21,2:15:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,粉色的 好可爱
Dialogue: 0,2:15:06.27,2:15:08.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,平时自己玩都用什么来着
Dialogue: 0,2:15:09.27,2:15:10.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吮吸器之类的
Dialogue: 0,2:15:10.53,2:15:11.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吮吸器啊
Dialogue: 0,2:15:11.77,2:15:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然有呢
Dialogue: 0,2:15:13.22,2:15:14.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个果然很爽吧
Dialogue: 0,2:15:14.99,2:15:16.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:15:19.61,2:15:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,鼻祖呢
Dialogue: 0,2:15:23.03,2:15:24.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个是鼻祖啊
Dialogue: 0,2:15:24.37,2:15:25.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧
Dialogue: 0,2:15:29.80,2:15:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,2:15:34.22,2:15:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么用
Dialogue: 0,2:15:41.71,2:15:44.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从这开始吗
Dialogue: 0,2:15:44.66,2:15:46.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,2:15:55.99,2:15:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟是鼻祖嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:16:16.09,2:16:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真可爱
Dialogue: 0,2:16:18.75,2:16:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电动棒之类的倒用过 但跳蛋还真没用过呢
Dialogue: 0,2:16:22.26,2:16:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细想想 确实
Dialogue: 0,2:16:24.55,2:16:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好像还没用过跳蛋呢
Dialogue: 0,2:16:26.32,2:16:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,电动棒倒是用过
Dialogue: 0,2:16:39.56,2:16:42.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,内裤露出来了
Dialogue: 0,2:16:54.15,2:16:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,马上就进入状态了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:16:56.20,2:16:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进入状态了吗
Dialogue: 0,2:16:56.77,2:16:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经发情了嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:16:57.90,2:16:59.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才都叫出那种声音了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:16:59.13,2:17:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没叫哦
Dialogue: 0,2:17:00.32,2:17:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你叫了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:17:00.47,2:17:02.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没叫啦
Dialogue: 0,2:17:06.20,2:17:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,2:17:12.74,2:17:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喜欢这种地方吗
Dialogue: 0,2:17:21.36,2:17:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要自己弄吗
Dialogue: 0,2:17:54.17,2:17:56.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天是最后了
Dialogue: 0,2:17:57.39,2:17:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,期待吗
Dialogue: 0,2:18:00.97,2:18:03.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变得最色了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:18:42.61,2:18:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,内裤湿了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:18:44.77,2:18:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湿了
Dialogue: 0,2:18:45.95,2:18:47.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湿了吗
Dialogue: 0,2:18:54.47,2:18:58.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样才够色啊
Dialogue: 0,2:19:00.83,2:19:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好色
Dialogue: 0,2:19:07.56,2:19:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服的地方
Dialogue: 0,2:19:08.71,2:19:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服的地方
Dialogue: 0,2:19:11.62,2:19:13.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这里吗
Dialogue: 0,2:19:27.29,2:19:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,2:19:57.35,2:19:59.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,挺好的嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:20:00.76,2:20:03.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像快睡着了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:20:04.87,2:20:07.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 你放松就好
Dialogue: 0,2:21:01.23,2:21:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好色哦
Dialogue: 0,2:21:02.57,2:21:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在动吗
Dialogue: 0,2:21:03.23,2:21:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还在动
Dialogue: 0,2:22:58.55,2:23:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好刺激
Dialogue: 0,2:24:54.89,2:24:56.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,豆豆变得超大了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:24:56.47,2:24:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: 0,2:25:44.96,2:25:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放进去了嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:25:46.03,2:25:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,放进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:25:56.64,2:25:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要夹在里面吗
Dialogue: 0,2:25:57.57,2:25:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,夹在里面
Dialogue: 0,2:25:59.66,2:26:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,2:27:02.16,2:27:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:27:03.76,2:27:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,情趣酒店里有好东西呢
Dialogue: 0,2:27:08.80,2:27:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个挺好的吧
Dialogue: 0,2:27:12.06,2:27:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能一直用嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:27:16.42,2:27:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舔舔它 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,2:27:17.90,2:27:19.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能好好享受了
Dialogue: 0,2:27:22.50,2:27:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已经睡着了吗
Dialogue: 0,2:27:23.69,2:27:24.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,2:27:38.10,2:27:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要穿角色扮演的衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,2:27:39.52,2:27:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿！！！
Dialogue: 0,2:27:41.73,2:27:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,护士服 或者啦啦队服
Dialogue: 0,2:27:46.44,2:27:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,种类还挺多呢
Dialogue: 0,2:27:51.58,2:27:52.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啦啦队
Dialogue: 0,2:27:52.52,2:27:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想穿啦啦队的吗
Dialogue: 0,2:27:55.80,2:27:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想穿啦啦队的
Dialogue: 0,2:28:04.30,2:28:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要穿啦啦队服吗
Dialogue: 0,2:28:14.01,2:28:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尺寸合适吗
Dialogue: 0,2:28:15.58,2:28:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,2:28:17.02,2:28:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:28:26.41,2:28:28.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是这种款式呢
Dialogue: 0,2:28:29.19,2:28:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不觉得很舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,2:28:30.67,2:28:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,滑溜溜的
Dialogue: 0,2:28:32.87,2:28:36.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,摸起来手感很好的样子
Dialogue: 0,2:28:46.11,2:28:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真合身
Dialogue: 0,2:28:48.79,2:28:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,简直像为你量身定做的嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:28:50.32,2:28:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个吗
Dialogue: 0,2:28:51.29,2:28:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如胸部的尺寸之类的
Dialogue: 0,2:28:55.49,2:28:58.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可爱的胸部穿着刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,2:28:58.91,2:29:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面也是吗
Dialogue: 0,2:29:00.53,2:29:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下面？ 把内裤脱了吧
Dialogue: 0,2:29:02.33,2:29:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不穿内裤直接穿不就好了
Dialogue: 0,2:29:12.44,2:29:14.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想试试不穿内裤
Dialogue: 0,2:29:27.72,2:29:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 那里可能刚好
Dialogue: 0,2:29:32.14,2:29:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 超级色
Dialogue: 0,2:29:35.77,2:29:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,2:29:38.09,2:29:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超级色哦
Dialogue: 0,2:29:43.93,2:29:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好像兴致很高嘛
Dialogue: 0,2:29:55.82,2:29:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吗
Dialogue: 0,2:31:38.27,2:31:39.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不错不错
Dialogue: 0,2:31:44.67,2:31:46.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啦啦队服真不错呢
Dialogue: 0,2:32:43.00,2:32:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,慢慢来哦
Dialogue: 0,2:33:15.96,2:33:19.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行 受不了了
Dialogue: 0,2:35:39.84,2:35:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可爱吗
Dialogue: 0,2:35:45.06,2:35:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可爱
Dialogue: 0,2:36:07.11,2:36:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,2:40:24.02,2:40:25.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样不行啊
Dialogue: 0,2:40:25.76,2:40:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才一下就插到最深处了吧
Dialogue: 0,2:40:39.00,2:40:40.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,舒服吗
Dialogue: 0,2:42:12.04,2:42:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,2:43:53.57,2:43:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,2:43:57.11,2:43:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,受不了了
Dialogue: 0,2:45:04.88,2:45:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,湿漉漉的了呢
Dialogue: 0,2:45:10.25,2:45:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要插进去吗
Dialogue: 0,2:45:11.07,2:45:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,肉棒
Dialogue: 0,2:45:13.91,2:45:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么插
Dialogue: 0,2:45:19.85,2:45:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 没事
Dialogue: 0,2:45:39.58,2:45:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把肉棒插进来
Dialogue: 0,2:45:42.48,2:45:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,插进来
Dialogue: 0,2:45:44.00,2:45:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蹭一蹭 磨一磨
Dialogue: 0,2:45:51.37,2:45:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试着一点一点插进去
Dialogue: 0,2:46:15.57,2:46:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的插法真色啊
Dialogue: 0,2:46:18.31,2:46:20.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要插进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,2:46:58.37,2:47:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,2:58:15.95,2:58:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久等了
Dialogue: 0,3:10:00.77,3:10:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,腿缠在一起了
Dialogue: 0,3:10:03.53,3:10:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,动不了了啦
Dialogue: 0,3:10:05.60,3:10:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样不挺好的吗
Dialogue: 0,3:10:07.23,3:10:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个…… 有点
Dialogue: 0,3:10:25.89,3:10:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,双腿缠上来点
Dialogue: 0,3:10:30.19,3:10:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,3:10:31.09,3:10:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贴紧点
Dialogue: 0,3:11:00.51,3:11:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: 0,3:11:07.99,3:11:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行了 不行了
Dialogue: 0,3:11:15.35,3:11:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,3:11:26.19,3:11:28.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉好多
Dialogue: 0,3:11:30.71,3:11:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射出好多
Dialogue: 0,3:11:40.67,3:11:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一起高潮好吗
Dialogue: 0,3:11:48.91,3:11:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要去了
Dialogue: 0,3:11:52.49,3:11:55.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要射了
Dialogue: 0,3:12:44.31,3:12:47.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最后那下刚刚好
Dialogue: 0,3:12:48.82,3:12:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很兴奋吗
Dialogue: 0,3:12:51.68,3:12:54.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了好多
Dialogue: 0,3:12:54.58,3:12:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了好多出来
Dialogue: 0,3:13:01.21,3:13:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,3:13:09.54,3:13:12.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刚好呢
Dialogue: 0,3:13:20.71,3:13:22.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,3:13:25.27,3:13:28.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这次旅行 我们做了好多次呢
Dialogue: 0,3:13:29.09,3:13:30.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做了好多次
Dialogue: 0,3:13:30.89,3:13:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很开心 做完马上又想做了呢
Dialogue: 0,3:13:33.99,3:13:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,毕竟很久没见了
Dialogue: 0,3:13:36.87,3:13:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是久违的旅行
Dialogue: 0,3:13:39.43,3:13:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得最棒的是什么
Dialogue: 0,3:13:40.87,3:13:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都很棒啦 不过……
Dialogue: 0,3:13:45.31,3:13:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是很喜欢看动物呢
Dialogue: 0,3:13:49.51,3:13:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃海鲜之类的也很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,3:13:52.93,3:13:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全都喜欢
Dialogue: 0,3:13:54.09,3:13:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得你吃东西的时候特别乖
Dialogue: 0,3:13:56.03,3:13:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,3:13:56.87,3:13:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感觉很温柔什么的
Dialogue: 0,3:14:04.45,3:14:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直在拍吗
Dialogue: 0,3:14:08.71,3:14:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,确实今天一直被拍着
Dialogue: 0,3:14:13.65,3:14:16.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不管做什么都真的很可爱
Dialogue: 0,3:14:16.53,3:14:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你还真会说话啊
Dialogue: 0,3:14:19.42,3:14:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过很开心
Dialogue: 0,3:14:20.95,3:14:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,3:14:23.75,3:14:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次再一起去旅行吧
Dialogue: 0,3:19:17.14,3:19:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干嘛…… 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,3:19:21.60,3:19:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,觉得刺眼吗
Dialogue: 0,3:19:23.82,3:19:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没睡着吗
Dialogue: 0,3:19:26.02,3:19:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,3:19:32.09,3:19:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得睡不着了
Dialogue: 0,3:19:33.42,3:19:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,3:19:41.20,3:19:42.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事 你睡吧
Dialogue: 0,3:19:42.53,3:19:43.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接着睡没关系的
Dialogue: 0,3:19:44.45,3:19:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,3:19:49.71,3:19:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这里变成这样了 睡不着了
Dialogue: 0,3:19:53.35,3:19:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又想做了吗
Dialogue: 0,3:19:57.19,3:19:58.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天？
Dialogue: 0,3:19:59.69,3:20:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等到明天啦
Dialogue: 0,3:20:01.16,3:20:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这样……
Dialogue: 0,3:20:03.77,3:20:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但就是睡不着了
Dialogue: 0,3:20:05.38,3:20:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,睡不着吗
Dialogue: 0,3:20:11.13,3:20:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真睡不着啊
Dialogue: 0,3:20:15.05,3:20:16.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到你没穿内裤
Dialogue: 0,3:20:23.62,3:20:25.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帮你弄出来吗
Dialogue: 0,3:20:31.36,3:20:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你没办法
Dialogue: 0,3:20:35.15,3:20:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都没怎么碰呢
Dialogue: 0,3:20:38.07,3:20:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都有味道了
Dialogue: 0,3:20:46.84,3:20:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,3:21:52.50,3:21:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,变硬了
Dialogue: 0,3:22:14.54,3:22:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,3:22:17.54,3:22:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 稍微有点……
Dialogue: 0,3:22:37.48,3:22:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快受不了了吧
Dialogue: 0,3:24:10.29,3:24:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,3:25:08.42,3:25:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,3:26:01.01,3:26:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要含到最深处去了吗
Dialogue: 0,3:26:12.73,3:26:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,3:26:38.88,3:26:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吃吗
Dialogue: 0,3:26:47.82,3:26:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多舔舔
Dialogue: 0,3:26:54.02,3:26:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好可爱
Dialogue: 0,3:27:56.19,3:27:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好胀好胀
Dialogue: 0,3:27:58.89,3:28:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很受不了吧
Dialogue: 0,3:29:18.76,3:29:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦 可以的
Dialogue: 0,3:29:32.59,3:29:34.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,3:29:39.28,3:29:41.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快不行了吗
Dialogue: 0,3:29:52.13,3:29:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,3:29:58.12,3:30:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,射了好多出来
Dialogue: 0,3:30:01.94,3:30:04.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明刚才才射过
Dialogue: 0,3:30:04.23,3:30:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害呢
Dialogue: 0,3:30:08.58,3:30:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到能射这么多
Dialogue: 0,3:30:16.07,3:30:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好胀
Dialogue: 0,3:30:19.35,3:30:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天还要早起 快睡吧
Dialogue: 0,3:30:24.05,3:30:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,3:30:30.26,3:30:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一起帮你擦了 稍微等一下
Dialogue: 0,3:30:37.19,3:30:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真厉害呢
